# ⚠️  SECURITY WARNING
# Do NOT put a real API key here for public/distributed builds.
# Vite bakes this value into dist/assets/popup.js in PLAIN TEXT.
# This file is safe to commit (it contains no real secrets).
#
# For local development only:
# VITE_OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-your-key-here
#
# For production: leave this blank.
# Users enter their own API key via the onboarding screen.
# It is stored securely in chrome.storage.local (never synced to Google).
VITE_OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
